post.body:
this is a truth for so many things in this world. for most businesses if not all, location is king. why?

- not just because it gives you traffic, as you know for convenience stores;
- not just because it gives you people, as you know for the sillicon valley;
- not just because it is a nice place so you can enjoy life;
- but because it gives you a place that you can call your home for many generations; and only this kind of location is a worthy location.
